{
  "id": "rules_glossary/s/spirit_keyword",
  "lookup_group": "rules_glossary",
  "lookup_id": "spirit_keyword",
  "title": "Spirit (Keyword)",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Cards with the spirit keyword represent the spirits of nature and the ancestors who dwell, unseen by most, in the Valley. By journeying to the spirit realm,"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Spirit Speakers"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/s/spirit_speaker_specialty",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/S/spirit_speaker"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "are able to communicate with these interdimensional beings and ask for their assistance with the task at hand."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You cannot interact with cards with the spirit keyword with any"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "common test"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/c/common_test",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/C/common_tests"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note: Other tests can still interact with spirits as normal."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Only"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "attachments"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/a/attachments",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/A/attachment"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "with the Spiritual trait can be attached to cards with the spirit keyword."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "items": [],
